<script id="wix-first-paint">
    if (window.ResizeObserver &&
        (!window.PerformanceObserver || !PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes || PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes.indexOf('paint') === -1)) {
        new ResizeObserver(function (entries, observer) {
            entries.some(function (entry) {
                var contentRect = entry.contentRect;
                if (contentRect.width > 0 && contentRect.height > 0) {
                    requestAnimationFrame(function (now) {
                        window.wixFirstPaint = now;
                        dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('wixFirstPaint'));
                    });
                    observer.disconnect();
                    return true;
                }
            });
        }).observe(document.body);
    }
</script>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Value Add: Identified key causes and affected commodities, enabling stakeholders to engage vendors with focused findings and drive remediation efforts.</p>
</li>
</ul></div><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9h8y8" class="KaEeLN comp-mhh9h8y8"><div class="uYj0Sg wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9h8y8inlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9h8y8inlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9h8yd" class="jbrj02 comp-mhh9h8yd"><div class="IvR70V wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9h8ydinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9h8ydinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9h8yd3" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9h8yd3 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_6 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">EG Thermal Analysis</span></h2></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9h8ye4" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9h8ye4 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:14px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Full-Stack Developer</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9h8yf4" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9h8yf4 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:1.5em; font-size:17px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Technologies: Python, SQL, Excel, Data Wrangling, PolyAnalyst &amp; Visualization</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9h8yg2" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9h8yg2 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><ul class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Problem Statement: Analysis required of thermal, blown, overheat &amp; sensor issue data for top 50 customers to surface key failure patterns.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Solution: Consolidated diverse case-notes via keyword/synonym matching, extracted relevant features (incident rate, cause, commodity failure, error code), and built a dashboard enabling management to visualise issue occurrence by dimension.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Value Add: Delivered clear visibility into thermal-related failures and highlighted key case-lists for stakeholders  supporting faster vendor escalation and remediation.</p>
</li>
</ul></div><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r1hd" class="KaEeLN comp-mhh9r1hd"><div class="uYj0Sg wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9r1hdinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9r1hdinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r1hl" class="jbrj02 comp-mhh9r1hl"><div class="IvR70V wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9r1hlinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9r1hlinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r1hm2" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9r1hm2 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_6 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Proactive Monitoring Tool</span></h2></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r1ho" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9r1ho wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:14px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Full-Stack Developer</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r1hp" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9r1hp wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:1.5em; font-size:17px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Technologies: Python, Excel/VBA, PolyAnalyst</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r1hq" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9r1hq wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><ul class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Problem Statement: Automatically generated alerts for critical issues (such as power-supply failures, fan &amp; system-board issues) across the top 50 customers required consolidation and prioritisation.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Solution: Developed a full-stack tool to extract key dimensions from case-notes using synonym-based matching, and delivered a dashboard with weekly auto-updates highlighting critical error-codes among system-generated cases.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Value Add: Provided stakeholders with a curated list of high-severity cases, enabling faster remediation and improved operational visibility.</p>
</li>
</ul></div><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r9bi" class="KaEeLN comp-mhh9r9bi"><div class="uYj0Sg wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9r9biinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9r9biinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r9bm2" class="jbrj02 comp-mhh9r9bm2"><div class="IvR70V wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9r9bm2inlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9r9bm2inlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r9bn2" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9r9bn2 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_6 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">One Report Tool (ORT)</span></h2></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r9bo4" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9r9bo4 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:14px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Full-Stack Developer</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r9bp3" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9r9bp3 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:1.5em; font-size:17px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Technologies: C#, SQL, VBA, Excel Automation</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r9bq1" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9r9bq1 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><ul class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Problem Statement: Multiple audit processes required extensive manual effort for data handling, reporting and analysis across accuracy, duration and reason audits.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Solution: Designed and developed a comprehensive full-stack tool integrating all audit processes data deduplication, random sampling, data upload (via Excel or tool interface), reporting, visualization and RCA analysis. Incorporated live PA data for potential-miss audits, automated charts, and added a custom audit feature for multi-filter allocations (reason, commodity, case type, cause, etc.).</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Value Add: Unified six audit processes within a single platform, enabling live data access, reducing manual effort, and improving data accuracy and reporting efficiency.</p>
</li>
</ul></div><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vgah" class="KaEeLN comp-mhh9vgah"><div class="uYj0Sg wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vgahinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vgahinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vgam" class="jbrj02 comp-mhh9vgam"><div class="IvR70V wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vgaminlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vgaminlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vgan" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vgan wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_6 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Database Administration for ORT</span></h2></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vgao" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vgao wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:14px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Full-Stack Developer</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vgap" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vgap wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:1.5em; font-size:17px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Technologies: SQL Server, Stored Procedures, Database Migration</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vgaq" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vgaq wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><ul class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Problem Statement: A customer experience database required setup, migration, and ongoing performance management to support real-time analytics and reporting.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Solution: Installed and maintained the SQL Server database for ORT; designed tables, views and stored procedures to manage data extraction and insertion; migrated data from local desktop to server environment; monitored database efficiency, upgraded existing structures, ensured access, uptime and data integrity; planned and coordinated storage and capacity requirements.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Value Add: Ensured robust, high-performance database infrastructure supporting live audit tooling, enhancing data reliability and operational efficiency.</p>
</li>
</ul></div><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vl8o" class="KaEeLN comp-mhh9vl8o"><div class="uYj0Sg wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vl8oinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vl8oinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vl8t" class="jbrj02 comp-mhh9vl8t"><div class="IvR70V wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vl8tinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vl8tinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vl8t3" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vl8t3 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_6 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Attribute Measurement System</span></h2></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vl8u4" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vl8u4 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:14px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Full-Stack Developer</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vl8v4" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vl8v4 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:1.5em; font-size:17px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Technologies: InfoPath, SharePoint Designer, VBA</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vl8w3" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vl8w3 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><ul class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Problem Statement: Correlation analysis was needed to compare case-categorisation decisions between team members and SMEs.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Solution: Developed a full-stack assessment tool using InfoPath forms for user input, SharePoint Designer workflows and VBA scripting to compute performance comparisons (team member vs SME vs team), validate data, and visualise results.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Value Add: Delivered an automated assessment and reporting workflow, enabling transparent performance comparisons and improving efficiency in categorisation processes.</p>
</li>
</ul></div><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--></div></section><!--/$--></div></div></section><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--></div></div></div></div></main><footer id="SITE_FOOTER" class="AT7o0U SITE_FOOTER wixui-footer" tabindex="-1"><div class="lvxhkV"></div><div class="cKxVkc"><div class="vlM3HR"></div><div class="VrZrC0"><div data-mesh-id="SITE_FOOTERinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="SITE_FOOTERinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><!--$--><section id="comp-k0kphh2d" class="comp-k0kphh2d CohWsy wixui-column-strip"><div id="bgLayers_comp-k0kphh2d" data-hook="bgLayers" data-motion-part="BG_LAYER comp-k0kphh2d" class="if7Vw2"><div data-testid="colorUnderlay" class="tcElKx i1tH8h"></div><div id="bgMedia_comp-k0kphh2d" data-motion-part="BG_MEDIA comp-k0kphh2d" class="wG8dni"></div></div><div data-testid="columns" class="V5AUxf"><!--$--><div id="comp-k0kphh32" class="comp-k0kphh32 YzqVVZ wixui-column-strip__column"><div id="bgLayers_comp-k0kphh32" data-hook="bgLayers" data-motion-part="BG_LAYER comp-k0kphh32" class="MW5IWV"><div data-testid="colorUnderlay" class="LWbAav Kv1aVt"></div><div id="bgMedia_comp-k0kphh32" data-motion-part="BG_MEDIA comp-k0kphh32" class="VgO9Yg"></div></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-k0kphh32inlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-k0kphh32inlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><!--$--><div id="comp-k2398tck" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-k2398tck wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_9 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:14px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"> 2035 by Jayanthan Rajendran.<br class="wixui-rich-text__text">

<script id="wix-first-paint">
    if (window.ResizeObserver &&
        (!window.PerformanceObserver || !PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes || PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes.indexOf('paint') === -1)) {
        new ResizeObserver(function (entries, observer) {
            entries.some(function (entry) {
                var contentRect = entry.contentRect;
                if (contentRect.width > 0 && contentRect.height > 0) {
                    requestAnimationFrame(function (now) {
                        window.wixFirstPaint = now;
                        dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('wixFirstPaint'));
                    });
                    observer.disconnect();
                    return true;
                }
            });
        }).observe(document.body);
    }
</script>

<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Solution: Crafted a pipeline that extracted complaint data, normalised key dimensions (IssueSignature, SymptomFact, SymptomConclusion, TroubleshootingAction, ResolutionAction, PartsConsumption) via predefined synonym sets, classified complaints into high-cardinality attributes (CaseType, Cause, Commodity, Reason, RF_Category) and delivered a daily auto-email Excel dashboard with attached visualisations.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Value Add: Provided timely insights into customer experience, enabled proactive reduction of multi-part failures and minimised warranty/part-replacement costs.</p>
</li>
</ul></div><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9h434" class="KaEeLN comp-mhh9h434"><div class="uYj0Sg wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9h434inlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9h434inlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9h439" class="jbrj02 comp-mhh9h439"><div class="IvR70V wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9h439inlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9h439inlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9h4393" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9h4393 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_6 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Analysis of Intel Processor Vulnerability</span></h2></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9h43a4" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9h43a4 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:14px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Full-Stack Developer</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9h43b3" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9h43b3 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:1.5em; font-size:17px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Technologies: PolyAnalyst, Python, Data Wrangling, Visualization</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9h43c1" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9h43c1 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><ul class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Problem Statement: Investigated instances of Meltdown &amp; Spectre vulnerabilities across Intelbased servers to isolate root causes.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Solution: Transformed unstructured textual data into actionable dimensions (e.g., Fan Status, Sensor Status, Overheat Level mapped to low/medium/high, Error Code); applied vocabulary &amp; phrase-matching to classify issues and mined patterns for correlation.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Value Add: Identified key causes and affected commodities, enabling stakeholders to engage vendors with focused findings and drive remediation efforts.</p>
</li>
</ul></div><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9h8y8" class="KaEeLN comp-mhh9h8y8"><div class="uYj0Sg wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9h8y8inlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9h8y8inlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9h8yd" class="jbrj02 comp-mhh9h8yd"><div class="IvR70V wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9h8ydinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9h8ydinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9h8yd3" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9h8yd3 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_6 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">EG Thermal Analysis</span></h2></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9h8ye4" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9h8ye4 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:14px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Full-Stack Developer</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9h8yf4" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9h8yf4 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:1.5em; font-size:17px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Technologies: Python, SQL, Excel, Data Wrangling, PolyAnalyst &amp; Visualization</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9h8yg2" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9h8yg2 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><ul class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Problem Statement: Analysis required of thermal, blown, overheat &amp; sensor issue data for top 50 customers to surface key failure patterns.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Solution: Consolidated diverse case-notes via keyword/synonym matching, extracted relevant features (incident rate, cause, commodity failure, error code), and built a dashboard enabling management to visualise issue occurrence by dimension.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Value Add: Delivered clear visibility into thermal-related failures and highlighted key case-lists for stakeholders  supporting faster vendor escalation and remediation.</p>
</li>
</ul></div><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r1hd" class="KaEeLN comp-mhh9r1hd"><div class="uYj0Sg wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9r1hdinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9r1hdinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r1hl" class="jbrj02 comp-mhh9r1hl"><div class="IvR70V wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9r1hlinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9r1hlinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r1hm2" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9r1hm2 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_6 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Proactive Monitoring Tool</span></h2></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r1ho" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9r1ho wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:14px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Full-Stack Developer</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r1hp" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9r1hp wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:1.5em; font-size:17px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Technologies: Python, Excel/VBA, PolyAnalyst</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r1hq" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9r1hq wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><ul class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Problem Statement: Automatically generated alerts for critical issues (such as power-supply failures, fan &amp; system-board issues) across the top 50 customers required consolidation and prioritisation.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Solution: Developed a full-stack tool to extract key dimensions from case-notes using synonym-based matching, and delivered a dashboard with weekly auto-updates highlighting critical error-codes among system-generated cases.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Value Add: Provided stakeholders with a curated list of high-severity cases, enabling faster remediation and improved operational visibility.</p>
</li>
</ul></div><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r9bi" class="KaEeLN comp-mhh9r9bi"><div class="uYj0Sg wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9r9biinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9r9biinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r9bm2" class="jbrj02 comp-mhh9r9bm2"><div class="IvR70V wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9r9bm2inlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9r9bm2inlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r9bn2" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9r9bn2 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_6 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">One Report Tool (ORT)</span></h2></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r9bo4" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9r9bo4 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:14px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Full-Stack Developer</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r9bp3" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9r9bp3 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:1.5em; font-size:17px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Technologies: C#, SQL, VBA, Excel Automation</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9r9bq1" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9r9bq1 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><ul class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Problem Statement: Multiple audit processes required extensive manual effort for data handling, reporting and analysis across accuracy, duration and reason audits.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Solution: Designed and developed a comprehensive full-stack tool integrating all audit processes data deduplication, random sampling, data upload (via Excel or tool interface), reporting, visualization and RCA analysis. Incorporated live PA data for potential-miss audits, automated charts, and added a custom audit feature for multi-filter allocations (reason, commodity, case type, cause, etc.).</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Value Add: Unified six audit processes within a single platform, enabling live data access, reducing manual effort, and improving data accuracy and reporting efficiency.</p>
</li>
</ul></div><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vgah" class="KaEeLN comp-mhh9vgah"><div class="uYj0Sg wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vgahinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vgahinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vgam" class="jbrj02 comp-mhh9vgam"><div class="IvR70V wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vgaminlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vgaminlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vgan" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vgan wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_6 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Database Administration for ORT</span></h2></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vgao" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vgao wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:14px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Full-Stack Developer</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vgap" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vgap wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:1.5em; font-size:17px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Technologies: SQL Server, Stored Procedures, Database Migration</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vgaq" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vgaq wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><ul class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Problem Statement: A customer experience database required setup, migration, and ongoing performance management to support real-time analytics and reporting.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Solution: Installed and maintained the SQL Server database for ORT; designed tables, views and stored procedures to manage data extraction and insertion; migrated data from local desktop to server environment; monitored database efficiency, upgraded existing structures, ensured access, uptime and data integrity; planned and coordinated storage and capacity requirements.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Value Add: Ensured robust, high-performance database infrastructure supporting live audit tooling, enhancing data reliability and operational efficiency.</p>
</li>
</ul></div><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vl8o" class="KaEeLN comp-mhh9vl8o"><div class="uYj0Sg wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vl8oinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vl8oinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vl8t" class="jbrj02 comp-mhh9vl8t"><div class="IvR70V wixui-box" data-testid="container-bg"></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vl8tinlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-mhh9vl8tinlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vl8t3" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vl8t3 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h2 class="font_6 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:20px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Attribute Measurement System</span></h2></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vl8u4" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vl8u4 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; font-size:14px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Full-Stack Developer</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vl8v4" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vl8v4 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_7 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:1.5em; font-size:17px;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Technologies: InfoPath, SharePoint Designer, VBA</span></p></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-mhh9vl8w3" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-mhh9vl8w3 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><ul class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Problem Statement: Correlation analysis was needed to compare case-categorisation decisions between team members and SMEs.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Solution: Developed a full-stack assessment tool using InfoPath forms for user input, SharePoint Designer workflows and VBA scripting to compute performance comparisons (team member vs SME vs team), validate data, and visualise results.</p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:14px;">Value Add: Delivered an automated assessment and reporting workflow, enabling transparent performance comparisons and improving efficiency in categorisation processes.</p>

			if (header) {
				const headerPosition = window.getComputedStyle(header).getPropertyValue('position').toLowerCase();
				const isHeaderStickyOrFixed = headerPosition === 'sticky' || headerPosition === 'fixed';
				headerOffsetHeight = isHeaderStickyOrFixed ? header.offsetHeight : 0;
			}

			document.documentElement.style.scrollPaddingTop = `${wixAdsOffsetHeight + headerOffsetHeight}px`;
        </script>
